snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio Pakistan is simply unparalleled. The songs are lyrically, rhythmically, visually in all sense so very appealing. Right from Par channa de, pasoori, kanyari, jhoom, peeche hutt, each song unique in its own way. You guys have set such high standards.
